# Domain — Velora

Internal UI kit path remains `src/components/SweetFlow/*`.

## Surfaces

| Surface | Route group | Users |
|---------|-------------|-------|
| Admin / back office | `(shell)` | owner, manager, inventory |
| POS | `(operational)/pos` | cashier (+ device pairing) |
| Auth / device / unlock | `(auth)` | all |
| Print | `(print)` | ops |
| Public menu | `/menu` | customers (no login) |

## Core domains (modules)

Customers, products/catalog, orders, purchases, inventory/transfers/stock-count, expenses, reports, dashboard, online-orders, loyalty, system/settings, auth.

## Tenancy

Org + multi-store. Active store via validated session/cookie (`sf_active_store`). All data access scoped by org; store-scoped where required.

## Roles (see `src/lib/constants.ts`)

`owner` · `manager` · `cashier` · `inventory` + fine-grained permissions / feature flags.

## Money & catalog

Currency formatting via shared helpers. Product images/logos in storage bucket `org-assets` when used.
